data.description: Welcome to this charming two-family home. Each unit boasts its own distinct character with ample living space and modern amenities. The first floor is duplexed to the lower level providing amazing space with 5beds & 2baths for a family that wants to stretch out or an investor that wants to maximize cashflow. The second floor features 2beds & 1bath with an open concept living room & dining room flowing into the kitchen. Fully occupied with the first floor lease ending June 2024 & the second floor being month to month. Walk into this great location and have access to parks within walking distance and this property also features 2 parking spaces. The property was rehabbed in 2019, Featuring: New stainless-steel appliances, New water tanks, New roof, New Plumbing, New electrical, New windows and more. Easy access to downtown Chicago being 10 miles away and a quick 20 min drive to Navy Pier. Schedule your appointment today to see this beautiful 2 Unit property!! (Property is currently fully occupied)
